          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "A typical 1.5 Ton AC consumes between 1,000 Watts (for a 5-star inverter model) and 1,800 Watts (for older or 3-star non-inverter models) under full load. The average hourly consumption of an inverter AC is lower (approx. 600-900W) once the room is cooled."
        }
